column1: The Pave Margot Set With A 1 Carat Round Lab Diamond
column3: Illuminate your most cherished moments with the brilliance of The Pave Margot engagement ring. The pave band, laden with shimmering diamonds, is just the beginning of the luminous journey. The true distinction lies in the pave diamonds seamlessly set into the prongs, amplifying the sparkle from every perspective and ensuring a radiant display of affection. Dive into a realm of major sparkle, where each diamond mirrors the countless precious moments you share.

column1: The Monica Set With A 1 Carat Round Lab Diamond
column3: The Monica is a true masterpiece that combines sleek refinement with icy sparkle. The centerpiece is a magnificent diamond that sparkles from every angle, surrounded by a glittering hidden halo that adds extra brilliance to the already stunning stone. The slender band is adorned with channel set baguette diamonds that perfectly complement the center stone. With its classic elegance and modern sophistication, The Monica engagement ring is the perfect way to celebrate your love story.

column1: The Low Profile Kamellie Set With A 1 Carat Round Lab Diamond
column3: Set with intricate pave diamonds, The Low Profile Kamellie blends the tastefully modern with a timeless classic. The hidden halo ensures there is sparkle coming in from every angle, highlighting your center stone and making it appear larger. The delicate design flatters the finger, while its low profile makes it practical for even the busiest hands.

column1: The Halo Stephanie Set With A 1 Carat Round Lab Diamond
column3: The Halo Stephanie is a stunning halo engagement ring that combines timeless elegance with contemporary brilliance. The vintage-inspired design adds a touch of romance and sophistication, making it the perfect choice for those who appreciate the charm of bygone eras, while the diamond halo enhances the center stone's brilliance, creating a dazzling display of light and sparkle. This ring is a celebration of love, style, and timeless beauty, making it the perfect choice for the moment you say, "Forever."

column1: The Nova Set With A 1 Carat Round Lab Diamond
column3: Introducing The Nova: a masterpiece of design that elevates the concept of the side stone engagement ring to dazzling new heights. Embrace the opportunity to make a bold statement of love with The Nova, a ring that promises to be as enduring and unforgettable as your love.

The setting boasts glittering brilliance from all angles, making your center stone appear larger while a slimming silhouette elongates the finger.
